race.comment: YEAH YOU (7) struggled to get involved last start after missing the jump at this track, but prior to that won by 2.75 lengths at this track (19.60) beating Lily Marleen in a T3 Grade 6 on November 14. Key runner on his best form. ELSIE DREAMING (2) was out of the placings last time when fifth at this track (19.77) but scored three back at this track (19.80). The form out of her last race has been franked. One of the better chances. SUPER SEALANT (1) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 2.5 lengths at Ballarat in a handy 22.74 beating Salmon Spray. Likely to be in the finish. BLAME ESMERALDA (8) generally performs well here at this distance.
